### Healthcheck
GET http://localhost:8000/health


### Login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}


### Me
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### List incomes
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/incomes
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### Create income
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/incomes
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 250000,
  "date": "2026-05-05",
  "category": "Salary",
  "type": "regular",
  "comment": "May salary"
}


### List expenses
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### Create expense
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 45000,
  "date": "2026-05-10",
  "category": "Food",
  "type": "variable",
  "recurrence_type": "none",
  "comment": "Groceries and cafes"
}


### List debts
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/debts
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### Create debt
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/debts
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Credit Card",
  "debt_type": "credit_card",
  "principal_balance": 100000,
  "annual_interest_rate": 24.9,
  "minimum_monthly_payment": 8000,
  "due_day": 12,
  "early_repayment_allowed": true,
  "payoff_priority": 1,
  "is_active": true,
  "comment": "Test credit card"
}


### Calculation summary
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calculations/summary?date_from=2026-04-01&date_to=2026-04-30
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### Cashflow
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calculations/cashflow?date_from=2026-04-01&date_to=2026-04-30
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### Debt strategy - avalanche
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calculations/debt-strategy
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "strategy_type": "avalanche",
  "start_date": "2026-04-01",
  "extra_monthly_payment": 15000,
  "max_months": 240
}


### Debt strategy - snowball
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calculations/debt-strategy
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "strategy_type": "snowball",
  "start_date": "2026-04-01",
  "extra_monthly_payment": 15000,
  "max_months": 240
}


### Scenario compare
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calculations/scenario-compare
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start_date": "2026-04-01",
  "max_months": 240,
  "scenarios": [
    {
      "strategy_type": "snowball",
      "extra_monthly_payment": 0
    },
    {
      "strategy_type": "snowball",
      "extra_monthly_payment": 15000
    },
    {
      "strategy_type": "avalanche",
      "extra_monthly_payment": 0
    },
    {
      "strategy_type": "avalanche",
      "extra_monthly_payment": 15000
    }
  ]
}


### Analytics overview
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/analytics/overview?date_from=2026-04-01&date_to=2026-04-30
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### Analytics income expense by month
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/analytics/income-expense-by-month?date_from=2026-01-01&date_to=2026-04-30
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### Analytics expense structure
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/analytics/expense-structure?date_from=2026-04-01&date_to=2026-04-30
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### Analytics debt dynamics
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/analytics/debt-dynamics?start_date=2026-04-01&strategy_type=avalanche&extra_monthly_payment=15000&max_months=120
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}